  <brief_title>Comparison Between Two Different Distention Medium in Diagnostic Hysteroscopy</brief_title>
  <official_title>CO2 or Physiological Solution as Distension Medium: Which One is Better in Diagnostic Hysteroscopy?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
