  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators aim to enroll 2000 patients to undergo diagnostic hysteroscopy for
      suspected uterine pathologies. Women will be randomized into two groups on the basis of
      distension medium : group A CO2; group B physiological solution. Pain discomfort will be
      evaluated after the examination.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
